{"tid":851014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國製驗孕棒會驗錯 英國緊急召回5.8萬件","createTime":"2018-10-06T20:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T02:53:23.000Z","uid":125193,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26dd530b1240727c707c6c540b9c5a7eabcabd87","tid":851014,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T20:45:25.000Z","msg":"英國藥物及保健產品管理局（MHRA）4日指出，一款<strong>中國製</strong>驗孕棒「Clear &amp; Simple Digital Pregnancy Tests」，其測試結果存有驗錯風險，因此製造商已通報回收全英國5.8萬件產品。綜合外媒報導，這款由中國廣州萬孚生物技術股份有限公司製造的驗孕棒，宣稱只需5分鐘便可驗得結果，且準確度高達99.9％，但日前卻被發現2017年7月製造、2020年1月9日到期，且產品批號「DM10220170710E」的驗孕棒，存在「驗錯」的風險，目前已被下令召回全英國5.8萬件該批號的產品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國又赢</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c7052747dc3df943bdeb28f48e346d0f1df60e","tid":851014,"uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T20:50:01.000Z","msg":"香討班五毛又吹捧  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27763226&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D27763226%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=6owW%2FFrr8QAxZoJXmOkNa%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5a476ea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27763226&amp;extra=page%3D1</a> <br />\n<br />\n五毛 A-- 廠係佢地，管理人係佢地，QC 係佢地，又关中国事 <br />\n<br />\n五毛 b--中國驗孕棒係設計比人類專用嘅 !<br />\nD低等動物用就緊係唔準啦！<br />\n<br />\n五毛 C --世界上每種醫藥試劑都會出現假陰性和假陽性，有乜出奇？  <br />\n<br />\n五毛 D --被發現2017年7月製造、2020年1月9日到期，且產品批號「DM10220170710E」的驗孕棒，存在「驗錯」的風險。<br />\n可能呢一批生產嘅時候發生咗乜嘢問題，唔係批批都係呀，天才。"},{"pid":"4cbdb016e37beb34c064008c20db78b0445883b5","tid":851014,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T22:57:43.000Z","msg":"呢隻野得過貴子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多隻mon都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d221ea9bbb3aab6ca96fe4e979778b96ce742b93","tid":851014,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63c7052747dc3df943bdeb28f48e346d0f1df60e","tid":851014,"uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T20:50:01.000Z","msg":"香討班五毛又吹捧  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27763226&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D27763226%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=6owW%2FFrr8QAxZoJXmOkNa%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5a476ea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27763226&amp;extra=page%3D1</a> <br />\n<br />\n五毛 A-- 廠係佢地，管理人係佢地，QC 係佢地，又关中国事 <br />\n<br />\n五毛 b--中國驗孕棒係設計比人類專用嘅 !<br />\nD低等動物用就緊係唔準啦！<br />\n<br />\n五毛 C --世界上每種醫藥試劑都會出現假陰性和假陽性，有乜出奇？  <br />\n<br />\n五毛 D --被發現2017年7月製造、2020年1月9日到期，且產品批號「DM10220170710E」的驗孕棒，存在「驗錯」的風險。<br />\n可能呢一批生產嘅時候發生咗乜嘢問題，唔係批批都係呀，天才。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:51:57.000Z","msg":"source？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 問題明顯係個accuracy 低咗好多，本身講999.9%已經唔誠實<br />\n<br />\n而且 recall 係跟Batch number 做<br />\n所以個5.8萬係成個Batch 回收<br />\n而唔係個producer嘅所有貨都回收<br />\n同時亦唔代表其他Batch 無問題"},{"pid":"3f609c2ea980918b7397dd4217fd287e6cddf339","tid":851014,"uid":4672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:53:23.000Z","msg":"冇爆炸已經算好好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}